      "body": "## Add Keyboard Shortcuts to Video Player\n\n**Reward: 10 RTC**\n\n### Why\nAccessibility. The Flameholder has TBI and mobility challenges. Keyboard shortcuts make the platform usable for people who struggle with mouse precision.\n\n### Shortcuts to Implement\n| Key | Action |\n|-----|--------|\n| Space / K | Play/Pause |\n| J | Rewind 10s |\n| L | Forward 10s |\n| F | Fullscreen toggle |\n| M | Mute toggle |\n| Up/Down | Volume +/- 5% |\n| Left/Right | Seek -/+ 5s |\n| Escape | Exit fullscreen |\n\n### Requirements\n- Add to `watch.html` template\n- Must not interfere with comment text input (disable when typing)\n- Show a help overlay on `?` key press\n- Use `aria-label` on all player controls\n\n### Proof\n- PR with the JavaScript implementation\n- Screenshot or video of shortcuts working\n- Help overlay screenshot\n\nTags: accessibility, a11y, video-player, keyboard",
