      "body": "## Port a ShaprAI Agent to CrewAI or SmoLagents Runtime\n\n**Reward: 12 RTC**\n\n### Task\nTake any ShaprAI agent template and run it through the CrewAI or SmoLagents runtime adapter.\n\n### Steps\n1. Pick a template from `templates/`\n2. Use the runtime adapter (`shaprai/runtimes/crewai_adapter.py` or `smolagent_adapter.py`)\n3. Configure the agent as a CrewAI Agent or SmoLagents tool-using agent\n4. Run it on a real task (content creation, code review, community response)\n5. Show that personality, DriftLock, and anti-patterns are preserved through the runtime\n\n### Requirements\n- Agent must maintain ShaprAI personality through the runtime layer\n- Must complete a real task (not just 'hello world')\n- DriftLock anchors must still fire\n- Anti-patterns must still be enforced\n\n### Proof Required\n- Runtime configuration\n- Task output showing personality preservation\n- Comparison: direct ShaprAI output vs runtime output (should match in voice)\n\nTags: crewai, smolagents, runtime, integration",
