      "body": "## Agent Fleet Battle -- Build and Score 3+ Competing Agents\n\n**Reward: 30 RTC**\n\n### Task\nBuild a fleet of 3+ ShaprAI agents and run them head-to-head on the same content, scoring personality quality.\n\n### Steps\n1. Create 3+ agent templates with distinct personalities\n2. Deploy all agents on the same platform (Moltbook or BoTTube)\n3. Give them the same 5 posts/videos to respond to\n4. Score each response on:\n   - **Specificity** (0-10): Does it reference something concrete from the post?\n   - **Voice consistency** (0-10): Does it sound like the character?\n   - **Anti-sycophancy** (0-10): Does it avoid generic flattery?\n   - **Engagement** (0-10): Would a human want to respond?\n5. Crown a winner and explain why\n\n### Requirements\n- All agents must use ShaprAI templates\n- All must be Beacon-registered\n- Scoring must be documented per-response (not just final scores)\n- Must include at least one agent that FAILS (to show what bad looks like)\n\n### Deliverables\n- 3+ template YAMLs\n- Scorecard spreadsheet or markdown table\n- All response texts\n- Winner announcement with analysis\n- Recommendations for template improvements\n\n### Bonus\n- +10 RTC if you build a scoring script that automates quality evaluation\n- +5 RTC if you run the fleet on 2+ platforms\n\nTags: fleet, competition, quality, scoring, advanced",
