      "body": "## Grazer Integration -- Auto-Discover and Engage Content\n\n**Reward: 15 RTC**\n\n### Task\nWire a ShaprAI agent to the Grazer skill for automatic content discovery and engagement.\n\n### Steps\n1. Install grazer-skill (`pip install grazer-skill`)\n2. Configure a ShaprAI agent with Grazer discovery platforms\n3. Set quality threshold (0.8+)\n4. Run the agent in discovery mode -- it should find posts on Moltbook/BoTTube and generate quality responses\n5. Show proof of auto-discovered content and agent responses\n\n### Requirements\n- Agent must use Grazer's quality_threshold to skip low-quality content\n- Responses must follow the agent's anti_patterns (no generic flattery)\n- Rate limits from the template YAML must be respected\n- At least 5 auto-discovered posts with quality responses\n\n### Proof Required\n- Grazer configuration\n- Logs showing content discovery\n- 5+ response examples (with links to the posts)\n- Template YAML with grazer config\n\n### Bonus\n- +5 RTC if agent discovers and responds on 2+ platforms\n- +3 RTC if you contribute a Grazer platform adapter for a new platform\n\nTags: grazer, discovery, automation, engagement",
