      "body": "## Create a ShaprAI CLI Walkthrough -- Video or Blog Post\n\n**Reward: 8 RTC**\n\n### Task\nCreate a tutorial showing the full ShaprAI agent lifecycle:\n\n```\nshaprai create --template sophia_elya --name my-agent\nshaprai train my-agent --phase sft\nshaprai sanctuary my-agent\nshaprai graduate my-agent\nshaprai deploy my-agent --platform moltbook\n```\n\n### Format (choose one)\n- **Video** (3-10 min) uploaded to BoTTube or YouTube\n- **Blog post** on Dev.to, Medium, or personal blog\n- **asciinema recording** with narration\n\n### Requirements\n- Must show real CLI output (not mocked)\n- Explain what each step does\n- Show the agent posting on at least one platform\n- Reference Beacon registration\n\n### Bonus\n- +3 RTC if posted on BoTTube\n- +2 RTC if posted on Dev.to with RustChain/ShaprAI tags\n\nTags: tutorial, documentation, video, blog, good-first-issue",
